description: Try our easy to follow Vegetti With Kale Pesto recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Salad,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Low salt,Seafood free,Gluten free,Egg free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Zucchini,Halal,High fibre,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Kale,Vegan,Asparagus,Dairy free
name: Vegetti With Kale Pesto Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Finely shred the zucchini, carrots and asparagus into thin ribbons. Place in a large bowl.
Process basil, kale, pine nuts and garlic in a food processor until finely chopped. With motor running gradually add oil and process until smooth. Drizzle over vegetables to serve.
